body:
Alright, so I have been a boards user for 2 years and have even called out people who appeal bans while their logs show bigotry, racism, sexism, bi-erasure, and all sorts of worldly evils. In my pursuit of vigilante justice, I have been extremely rude to these "humans" and have taken down those posts as a sign of solidarity to the community (you guys!) who have given me the most joy. NOW: onto my main point my ban should be overturned completely and absolutely. As previously established, I have been a loyal, active, and enlightened boards community member, for that alone this appeal is convincing. BUT: a little background info: my helpful teammate decided to INTENTIONALLY ban my otp (rengar). so i calm down, ground myself like da champ, fix my posture etc. and i say "ok let me try that funky ryze build my flatmate sent me on discord that other night at the deli". yeah uhh turns out the build is GARBAGE, no resists, no mana, little utility and its weak to drain tanks. DESPITE ALL OF THIS: I still had the most damage on my team by a large margin. is that not persistence or what? Despite all of this, I was banned........easy to say the system failed here

Conclusion: the only thing I can do now is ask riot to unban my account, 14 days is still 14 too many


{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
